<br>
Lvl....Dmg.....Mana <br>
<br>
39.....381.....180<br>
44.....606.....250<br>
49....1120.....400<br>
51.....643.....215<br>
54.....658.....215<br>
55.....663.....215<br>
57.....716.....215<br>
60....1615....450<br>
<br>
I dont see how were getting any stronger post 50, maybe its just me but the spells thru 51-59 are weaker than our 49 spell. sure they cast faster, but casting 2 ice comet is faster than casting 4 draughts for near equal damage.<br>
<br>
Not only that, Lure spells do significantly less damage for more mana AND is resisted tons of times on various bosses. (yes, there are mobs that are very resistant to all 3 types of lures..unlike verant thinks... 'All mobs in EQ are 0% resistant to a certain type of lure, u just need to find out which'. haha thats funny) i can think of so many mobs that are resistant to lures its not funny. some seem 100% resistant to all lures (drakes in sky 7th isle).<br>
<br>
recently added spells Hsagra's Wrath and Porlo's Fury is what they think would 'balance' us. omg then why is it so damn specific? Hsagra's Wrath is supposed to work only on giants. no wait, it only works on specific giants! only ones in SoV. oh, theres more.. it only works on specific giants that are in SoV, namely Velketor (maybe), Tormax and Vindicator. I'm sure Porlo's Fury works on very specific dragons too. <br>
<br>
the thought of us being useless until we hit 60, and still useless on all mobs except on a few, very specific bosses even after reaching 60, never seemed to have occured to the creative, hard working employees of verant<br>
<br>
whats more is, none of the other classes had to 'Quest' for their new spells. so how come we do? our new spells arent exceptional or anything heh. i was actually glad i didnt have to carry around stacks of peridots anymore since i got the epic.. guess i was wrong <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . <br>
<br>
in my opinion, to fix wizzies, they need to up the mana/dmg ratio from ice comet. up the dmg of spells from ice comet. and screw lures, make all our spells completely unresistable. not fair to other nukers? well we dont have pets, cant heal, cant buff, etc, etc. our only job is to nuke heh, cant do anything else. we should be noticeably better at it than mages, druids, etc... unlike how it is now <br>
<br>
dmg from ice comet should go up more like this.<br>
<br>
lvl 49 - 1120 dmg (ice comet)<br>
lvl 51 - 1300~ dmg (each lvl would make it 100 pts stronger)<br>
lvl 54 - 1700~ dmg<br>
lvl 55 - 1800~ dmg plus chance to interrupt (jiva)<br>
lvl 57 - 2100~ dmg<br>
lvl 60 - 3000~ dmg<br>
<br>
only way we can ever dream of outdmging melees post SoV imo. no, the dmg numbers were not thought out carefully, just an idea of where our dmg per shot should be. <br>
<br>
added to that should be critical hits too. this should have been put in long ago when war, rng, rog got it.<br>
<br>
after all, groups with WIZARDS should be the exp/ks group in raids. kinda getting annoying how we're shoved in left over groups with no healers heh (or go solo $$)<br>
